  ('dietitian-moex-08644', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-098-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關Ketone bodies之敘述，何者正確？', '["由liver所合成，可在hepatocytes經代謝再利用", "由於飲食中carbohydrate不足，而使cholesterol異常代謝而產生", "在liver中合成，而在extrahepatic tissue中被代謝利用", "包括acetoacetic acid、β-hydroxyisobutyric acid和acetone，後者不能被利用而經由lungs和kidneys 排出"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e6d9fb027d26", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c7bc2a7b664f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "098140", "c": "113", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "098", "exam_name": "098年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、營養師、醫師分試 、法醫師", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
